Hi! I'm Carlin! I'm 23 years old.

Little bio about myself;

I grew up in the twin cities area of Minnesota. I've been tinkering on computers since I was a young kid, cliche, I know. Got my degree in CS at North Dakota State University. While there, I was part of a small engineering fraternity, epsilon chapter of Sigma Phi Delta. During the last two years of college, I also worked at Scheels corporate, a midwest sporting goods retailer. There, I updated servers by night, learning all about Linux and system administration. I finished my degree, went full time for a bit, saved up enough to escape Fargo, ND and moved here to Seattle! The rest is still to unfold!
